  <div class="sb_box br-bg">
    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?2.html">潍博之信</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?3_1.html">规章制度</a></div>
      <span>规章制度</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">第十一章  财务管理</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">根据事业单位财务制度准则、会计出纳制度和本馆具体情况，规范本馆财务行为，加强财务管理，提高资金使用效益，保障财务工作有序进行。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财务管理</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">财务管理原则</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、财务科是组织、核实、反映和监督全馆预算资金收入、支出管理的唯一科室。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;2、经费支出须严格遵循勤俭办事原则，分清轻重缓急，统筹安排，合理地使用各项资金，确保本馆各项事业稳步健康发展。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、财务管理规定</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、各科室每年8月底前将本科室下一年度经费预算报至财务科，由财务科汇总、编制下一年度本馆的经费预算。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、各科室的每项业务支出经费，须提前编制准确的项目预算，由分管领导签字，报馆长审核批准后方可实施，严禁无预算、超预算支出。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、所需经费支出时，须提前报请分管馆长、馆长核准，方可支出。数额重大者，需报请馆长办公会议批准。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、支出单据报销须有两名经办人、分管领导、馆长签字，购置固定资产的单据支出，须持固定资产入库单，方能报销。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5、凡购买馆需物资，须使用公务卡支付，并附正式发票，否则不予报销。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;6、维护财会纪律，保证账款平衡，每月按时与银行核对账单，每月底主管会计与出纳员核对银行存款、现金余额是否与账面对应。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7、严禁以个人名义拆借公款，因公借款须经馆长签字，借款时间不能过当月。特殊情况不能按期还款的，需向财务科予以说明，否则，以挪用公款论处。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8、专项经费必须严格执行专款专用原则，不得以任何理由任意挤占、挪用专项经费。按时足额为全馆干部职工缴纳“五险一金”，及时为离休老干部报销发放医药费，按需为职工提取公积金等。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;9、在填报、编制财务预算、决算中，科学设置课目，积极争取财政经费。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;10、财务科人员须严格执行财会制度，努力增强服务意识，提高服务质量。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>1）须严格执行馆内各项规章制度，树立良好的社会道德和职业道德，要做到遵守财经纪律，执行会计制度，坚持原则，秉公办事，做好领导的参谋。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>2）做到日清日结，准确无误，并于每周一汇总好上星期的收支情况，以备待用；支出单据手续齐全方可报销，否则不与支付；每天库存限额不得超过1000元，超过部分及时送存银行。</span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>3）工作中要做到态度和蔼，服务热情，须事事、处处以身作则，遵纪守法，支持领导和其它科室工作；做好上级有关部门的日报、季报、年报和馆领导所需的业务资料，管好、用好预算内外所有有限资金，做好资金的后勤保障工作。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>4）工作中，如出现因推诿扯皮而造成不良影响，以及违犯财经制度和馆内各项规章制度造成损失的，按规定给予相应惩处。</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第三条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">差旅费管理</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">差旅费管理应保证出差合理有序，严格控制费用开支。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、差旅费是指工作人员因公到潍坊市城区（奎文区、潍城区、坊子区、寒亭区、高新区、保税区）以外地区公务出差所发生的费用，开支范围包括城市间交通费、住宿费、伙食补助费和市内交通费等。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、出差必须按规定报经馆领导批准，从严控制出差人数和天数。严格差旅费预算管理，控制差旅费开支规模；严禁无实质内容、无明确公务目的的差旅活动，严禁以任何名义和方式变相旅游，严禁异地部门间无实质内容的学习交流和考察调研。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、城市间交通费是指工作人员因公到潍坊市城区以外地区出差乘坐火车、轮船、飞机等交通工具所发生的费用。出差人员应当按有关规定乘坐交通工具。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、未按规定等级乘坐交通工具的，超支部分由个人自理。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、到出差目的地有多种交通工具可选择时，出差人员在不影响公务、确保安全的前提下，应当选乘经济快捷的交通工具。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、乘坐飞机的，民航发展基金、燃油附加费可凭据报销。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、乘坐飞机、火车、轮船等交通工具的，每人次可购买交通意外保险一份。所在单位统一购买交通意外保险的，不得重复购买。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、住宿费是指工作人员因公出差期间入住宾馆（包括酒店、饭店、招待所）发生的房租费用。住宿标准依据本馆财务规定执行。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">五、伙食补助费是指对工作人员在因公出差期间给予的伙食补助费用。补助标准依据本馆财务规定。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">六、市内交通费是指工作人员因公出差期间发生的市内交通费用。补助标准依据本馆财务规定。乘坐本单位公务用车出差的，不得报销市内交通费。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">七、工作人员出差结束后应当及时办理报销手续。差旅费报销时应当提供出差审批单、机票、车票、住宿费、发票等凭证。住宿差旅支出等按规定使用公务卡结算。当天往返潍坊市城区的，按规定报销除住宿以外的其他费用。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">八、财务科对差旅费报销进行审核把关，确保票据来源合法，内容真实、完整、合规。对未经批准擅自出差、不按规定开支和报销差旅费的人员进行严肃处理。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">九、出差人员不得向接待单位提出正常公务活动以外的要求，不得在出差期间接受违反规定用公款支付的宴请、非工作需要的参观，不得接受礼品、礼金和土特产品等。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第四条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会议费管理</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">会议召开应坚持厉行节约、反对浪费、规范简朴、务实高效原则，严格控制会议数量、规模，规范会议费管理，提高会议效率和质量。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、合理安排会议时间，严格控制会议规模，精减参会人员，不请与会议无关的单位和人员参会，工作人员控制在会议代表人数的</span>10%以内。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、会议费开支范围包括会议住宿费、伙食费、会议室租金、交通费、文件印刷费、医药费等。会议费定额标准，参照国家相关规定。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、会议费实行一会一结算制，会议结束后要及时办理报销手续。会议费报销时，要提供会议审批文件、会议通知及实际参会人员名单表、会议召开场所等会议服务单位提供的费用原始明细单据、电子结算单等凭证。财务部门要严格按规定审核会议费开支，对未经批准及超范围、超标准开支的经费不予报销。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、会议费支付应当严格按照国库集中支付制度和公务卡管理制度有关规定执行，以银行转账或公务卡方式结算，禁止以现金方式结算。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">五、严禁借会议名义组织会餐或安排宴请；严禁套取会议费设立</span>“小金库”；严禁在会议费中列支公务接待费。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">六、严格执行会议用房标准，以标准间为主；会议用餐安排自助餐或工作餐，严格控制菜品种类和数量，严禁提供高档菜肴，不安排宴请，不上烟酒；会议会场一律不摆花草，不制作背景板，不提供水果。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">七、不得使用会议费购置电脑、复印机、打印机、传真机等固定资产及开支与会议无关的其他费用；不得组织会议代表旅游和与会议无关的参观；严禁组织高消费娱乐、健身活动；严禁以任何名义发放纪念品；不得额外配发洗漱用品。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第五条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">培训费管理</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">举办培训应当坚持厉行节约、反对浪费原则，实行单位内部统一管理，增强针对性和时效性，确保培训质量，节约培训资源，提高培训经费使用效益。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、培训费是指开展培训直接发生的各项费用支出，包括住宿费、伙食费、培训场地费、讲课费、培训资料费、交通费、其它费用等。培训费定额标准，参照国家相关规定。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、严格执行培训审批制度，对制定的培训计划要按时上报主管部门、财政部门。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、组织培训应尽量利用网络、视频等信息化手段，大力推行自主选学、在职自学等方式，降低培训成本，提高培训效率。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、需安排集中培训的，应当在开支范围和开支标准内，择优选择培训机构。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">五、组织培训的工作人员控制在参训人员数量的</span>5%以内，最多不超过10人。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">六、要严格控制培训经费支出。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">七、严禁借培训名义安排公款旅游；严禁借培训名义组织会餐或安排宴请；严禁组织高消费娱乐、健身活动；严禁使用培训费购置电脑、复印机、打印机、传真机等固定资产以及开支与培训无关的其他费用；严禁在培训费中列支公务接待费、会议费；严禁套取培训费设立</span>“小金库”。</span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">八、培训结束后要及时办理报销手续。报销培训费应当提供培训通知、实际参训人员签到表、讲课费签收单以及培训机构出具的原始明细单据、电子结算单等凭证。财务科应当严格按照规定审核培训费开支，对未履行审批备案程序的培训，以及超范围、超标准开支的费用不予报销。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">九、讲课费、小额零星开支以外的培训费用，应当按照国库集中支付和公务卡管理的有关制度执行，采用银行转账或公务卡方式结算，不得以现金方式支付。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第六条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">专项资金管理</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">　</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">根据《中华人民共和国预算法》《山东省省级财政专项资金管理暂行办法》等法律、法规，规范和加强</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">馆的财政专项资金管理，提高资金使用效益。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:9px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">　</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财政专项资金，是指由国家、省、市级财政安排，支持</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">馆公共服务发展，服务于特定政策目标或者工作任务，在一定时期内具有专门用途的财政性资金。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">　　</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">专项资金申报、使用、监督各环节应当相互协调、相互制约，遵循依法管理、科学公正、权责对等、绩效优先、公开透明的原则。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">　</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">专项资金预算编制</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">馆</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">科</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">应当按照科学规范、突出重点、注重绩效、厉行节约的原则，编制和申报专项资金预算</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">申报的专项资金要符合本</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">馆</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发展规划，要进行充分的可行性论证和严格审核，按轻重缓急排序后上报市财政局</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">专项资金预算的申报项目必须按照市财政部门的要求填报项目预算和有关内容并附相关材料，申报材料的内容必须真实、准确、完整。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">五、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">专项资金预算执行</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">专项资金应当专款专用，任何部门和个人不得擅自变更专项资金用途。确需变更的，用款单位应当按照项目和资金管理权限逐级上报主管部门审批。重大变更事项应当逐级上报相关主管部门批准</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">项目完成后，及时组织有关部门进行验收和审计程序，如有结余资金，上报市财政部门，获批准后编入下一年度预算结转使用</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">六、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">专项资金绩效管理</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">按照</span>“预算编制有目标、预算执行有监控、预算完成有评价、评价结果有运用”的要求，专项资金实行全过程预算绩效管理</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;2、本馆</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">科</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在申报专项资金预算时，制定专项资金绩效目标，准确反映预期实现的效益和效果。市财政部门对专项资金预算编制批复后，下达给本</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">馆财务科</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，作为预算执行和绩效评价的重要依据。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第七条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡使用管理</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、根</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">据《山东省预算单位公务卡改革实施意见》（鲁财库【</span>2008】26号）文件规定，规范</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本馆</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">支付管理</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">减少现金支付结算</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">降低现金管理成本，提高财务管理水平</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">及</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">支付透明度。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡的申请办理</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡是</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本馆</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工作人员持有的，主要用于日常公务支出和财务报销业务的信用卡，具有普通信用卡的所有功能，享有一定透支额度与免息期</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡申请人应为</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">馆在职职工。申请人主动提出申办公务卡需求，与发卡银行签订申请协议。财务科协助向发卡银行提供、呈递相关资料</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡实行</span>“一人一卡”实名制管理，其法律责任主体为公务卡持卡人。卡片及密码由持卡人自选保管，并承担相应的法律责任。</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡开支范围</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡开支范围为：办公费、印刷费、差旅费、会议费、招待费、水电费、专用材料费、公务用车运行维护费等零星的商品和服务支出原则上应当使用公务卡结算。具体开支范围按照国家公布的公务卡结算目录执行，并随之调整</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">凡属于公务卡开支范围的公务支出项目，应按规定使用公务卡结算，原则上不再使用现金结算。原使用转账方式结算的，可继续使用转账方式</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">属于公务卡开支范围的支出，财务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">科</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一般情况下不再办理对职工个人的现金借款业务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">凡属公务卡开支范围而使用现金结算的支出，经手人应提供不能使用公务卡结算的证明材料或情况说明，并由证明人和部门负责人签字认可</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">持卡人持卡进行公务消费前，应按照审批程序向领导请示并获同意后，方可进行。未获批准的消费支出一律视为持卡人私人消费，由持卡人自行承担</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;6、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">原则上不允许通过公务卡提取现金进行公务消费。确有特殊需要，应于事前请示</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">主要</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">领导并获同意。未经同意提取现金而产生的相关费用，由持卡人自行承担。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡报销</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务支出发生后，持卡人应于</span>10日内凭POS机刷卡消费凭条、发票及相关附件等凭证，按照财务报销程序到财务</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">科</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">办理审核报销手续</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财务人员根据持卡人提供的刷卡消费凭条信息，查询并核对公务消费记录的真实性，审核无误后方可报销</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">科</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">应及时去银行办理持卡人公务卡还款业务，如因财务人员工作失误，延误还款造成的罚息和滞纳金，由财务人员承担相应责任</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">持卡人应自行查询、确认公务卡消费报销后的资金到账情况，若有异常，应及时向财务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">科</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">反馈</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">已报销的公务消费，因退货或其他原因，商家将货款退回原持卡人公务卡后，持卡人应积极配合财务科协助办理资金的退付手续</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;6、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">下列情况不得予以报销，发生费用由持卡人个人承担。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">报销费用与提供的报销凭证、消费交易凭条明显不符的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">报销时间超过免息期后产生的罚息、滞纳金等相关费用</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">因个人保管不善或遗失等原因，导致公务卡被盗刷卡所造成的支出</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>4）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">消费后无交易凭条或原始发票等形成的支出</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">　</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>5）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">其他不符合财务管理规定和要求的。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7、附则：</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>1）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">特殊情况下持卡人信用额度不能满足公务消费时，持卡人可向发卡行申请追加临时授信额度</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>2）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡在满足公务支出的前提下，也可用于个人消费结算，但单位不承担个人消费导致的一切责任</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>3）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公务卡遗失或损毁后，持卡人应及时到发卡行申请补办。</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>4）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">持卡人调动、离职、退休或其他特殊原因，应及时与发卡行协调，办理终止该信用卡的公务消费及报销的相关手续</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>5）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">持卡人应遵守国家关于银行卡使用管理的法律法规，规范使用公务卡。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第八条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">本馆所进行的政府采购行为，均严格按照《山东省政府采购管理办法》（山东省人民政府令第</span>262号）等法律、法规进行，严格规范本馆政府采购行为，提高采购质量和效率，保障本馆各项工作健康有序开展。</span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=469"></script></div>
      
